abstract: The Vermont senator returned to the campaign trail, with Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez and Michael Moore in tow.
lead_paragraph: AMES, Iowa â€” The impeachment trial scrambled plans for the senators competing in the Democratic primary race. They would normally be blitzing Iowa in the final days before the caucuses, but they instead spent much of the past week in Washington, serving as jurors for the trial of President Trump, before returning to Iowa on Saturday.
